{"tid":837663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到而家都唔撚明點解啲地鐵巴士office商場 可以凍撚成咁","createTime":"2018-09-26T14:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T14:33:18.000Z","uid":35857,"like":8,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fef9fc625b18b3a6ee6880d9a4c25b5e6cf20eda","tid":837663,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭車凍到低溫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個心跳得勁快 個人係咁震<br />\n寧願早兩個站落行返屋企 所以有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一到夏天就變撚哂雪房咁<br />\n着埋褸都仲係凍到仆街<br />\n尤其地鐵巴士 開都咁撚大冷氣<br />\n成日加價 點解唔減少consumption?<br />\n班環保撚又係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁耐以嚟乜鳩都冇做過<br />\n淨係識搞埋啲不切實際嘅走飲管<br />\n減少能源消耗就唔撚關環保事?<br />\n室內個啲仲慘 有時有野做要留成日 又唔走得人<br />\n凍足成日 命都短幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7d43f57d62573b100e71a4404de28b9366a31f","tid":837663,"uid":35908,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"adfb74948160854fd00336675017d6a59da50563","tid":837663,"uid":11995,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你虧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e9e13bbe15d8d900bb60af51469dae96568716","tid":837663,"uid":66158,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"地鐵凍你都講得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熱撚到閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8337401bb36d9ebe5aa98844ba00581edd268f93","tid":837663,"uid":144464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"凍可以著外套架，有無諗過熱底嘅人係咩感覺阿？？"},{"pid":"3bb8acdc48a26fca28b53b75d54dce3976a52c1e","tid":837663,"uid":35857,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c1